  "company.thesis.body1": "Nexa was born in Lima, Peru, with a team of engineers and supply chain operators. We saw first-hand the operational leakage that appears when cheese, charcuterie, and dairy distribution depends on disconnected logs, generic ERPs, and fragmented WhatsApp.",
  "company.thesis.body2": "We don't sell visionary promises. We deploy hard operational fixes. When you work with us, the team that converts your physical flow into reliable digital infrastructure works with you directly.",
